<h2 id="organisational-chart">Organisational chart</h2>

<p>The Companies House <span id="attachment_3206862" class="attachment-inline">
  <a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/776545/Companies_House_Org_Chart_V11.pdf">organisational chart</a>
  (<span class="type"><abbr title="Portable Document Format">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class="file-size">146KB</span>, <span class="page-length">1 page</span>)
</span>
 shows how our management is structured.</p>

<h2 id="main-board">Main board</h2>

<p>The main board:</p>

<ul>
  <li>consists of the chair, the chief executive, executive directors and non-executive board members</li>
  <li>handles all aspects of our organisation, including performance, finances and strategic direction</li>
  <li>reports to Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy on our governance, strategy, priorities and progress</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="members">Members</h3>

